column2: select top # spa.ra, spa.dec, spa.dered_r as magnitude,  spa.dered_g - spa.dered_r as colour, spa.class, spa.z,  soa.xfocal as x, soa.yfocal as y  from specphotoAll as spa join specObjAll as soa on soa.specObjID = spa.specObjID where spa.plate = #  and spa.dered_r > #  order by spa.dered_r asc
